body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, my name is Jesse Henderson and I'm a customer service representative at SafeRide Auto Dealership. May I please have your name?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Carol. How may I assist you today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'd like to inquire about security measures at your dealership.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Absolutely! Could you please provide me with your date of birth and phone number for verification purposes?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, my date of birth is one nine five five zero two zero three.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you. And could you please provide your phone number as well?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: My phone number is seven eight zero- four five six- one two three four.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for providing that information, Carol. Is there anything else you would like to know about our security measures?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, that's all. Thank you for your help.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: You're welcome, Carol. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
